{
  "stem": "2581.8",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Don't take me to this work.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he sent me to chop wood, gave me a little spot and I chopped wood for him.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It so happens that during that time, I had a little bit more to eat.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "My father was inside, was laying in there in that sick bed with typhus.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So I would just go in, ask him how he his.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But once you're not hungry-- I wanted to sleep with my father.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Never got up.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Never got up from that bunker, which are these-- these were dug halfway underground and the bed was level with the ground.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And above the ground, you see only a little peek like that.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, I have a picture that the American soldiers made when they came to this camp.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Our particular camp was blown up, burned down, when they run away because the Americans were already close by, but that camp became a sick camp.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "A so-called hospital camp.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "It was so bad.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We were so hungry there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We were so cold.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I remember in '44 when the-- I don't know what month it was, but there was a little sun.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "We had no clothing, so I just had the blanket.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I went outside, barely walking, and I took the grass and sucked the grass, the juice, and spit it out.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "So hungry, so weak.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "That was a time where we knew that there is no way that we can survive.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "But I was with my father, and I said, I've got to help my father.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "It was the other way around.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And at that camp, they brought people and waited till they die.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Of course, at the beginning, there were things going on where you had-- at first it was the Algerian people.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
